# Supabase Configuration
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key

# Frontend URL (for payment redirect)
FRONTEND_URL=https://your-frontend-domain.com

# PortOne Payment API Credentials
# Apply for PortOne account at: https://portone.io/korea/ko
PORTONE_STORE_ID=store-xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
PORTONE_API_SECRET=your-api-secret-key

# Optional: Environment Configuration
ENVIRONMENT=development  # development | production

# =============================================================================
# PORTONE API ENDPOINTS (for reference)
# =============================================================================
# API Base URL:
#   - https://api.portone.io
#
# Key Endpoints:
#   - Get Payment: GET /payments/{paymentId}
#   - Cancel Payment: POST /payments/{paymentId}/cancel
#   - Webhook: Configured in PortOne dashboard
#
# Supported Payment Methods (via PortOne):
#   - 카카오페이 (KakaoPay)
#   - 토스페이 (TossPay)
#   - 네이버페이 (NaverPay)
#   - 페이코 (Payco)
#   - 신용/체크카드 (Credit/Debit Card)
#   - 실시간 계좌이체 (Bank Transfer)
#   - 가상계좌 (Virtual Account)
#
# Documentation: https://portone.gitbook.io/docs/
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================
# 1. Create a Supabase project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Get SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_ANON_KEY from project settings
# 3. Get SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY from project API settings (keep secure!)
# 4. Sign up for PortOne at https://portone.io/korea/ko
# 5. Create a Store (가맹점) in PortOne dashboard
# 6. Get PORTONE_STORE_ID and PORTONE_API_SECRET from PortOne dashboard
# 7. Configure payment methods in PortOne dashboard (KakaoPay, Toss, Naver, etc.)
# 8. Configure webhook URL in PortOne dashboard:
#    https://your-project.supabase.co/functions/v1/payment-webhook
# 9. Copy this file to .env and fill in actual values
# 10. Deploy functions: supabase functions deploy
#
# Benefits of PortOne:
#   - Multiple payment methods with single integration
#   - No monthly fee, only transaction fees (3.0-3.5%)
#   - Sandbox environment for testing (no business registration required)
#   - Easy PG provider switching
#   - Built-in recurring billing support
# =============================================================================
